Class ServiceConstraints

java.lang.Object
org.opengis.cite.iso19142.BaseFixture
org.opengis.cite.wfs20.nsg.testsuite.getcapabilities.ServiceConstraints
public class ServiceConstraints extends org.opengis.cite.iso19142.BaseFixture
Tests if the capabilities populates the Service Constraints of the OperationsMetadata document as described in Section 8.1.3.3.1. (see NSG WFS 2.0 Profile, 8.1.3.3.1 Service Constraints, Table 15 : WFS Service Constraints).
